init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But as the power grows, they realize that it's not a dream.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And they want to know how to control it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The most powerful of these teams, the Order, is led by the most powerful of all humans, the Mage.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And the Order is determined to do just that.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are able to hold the aliens at bay.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are looking for weaknesses in the enemy's defenses.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: vulnerable to certain types of magic.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Order is very careful about what they do next.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Order is ready to take the fight to the enemy.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Mage then orders the troops to attack.
